joinMessages.ExampleJoin:
{join.name} has joined the server! They created their account at {join.creationDate}.
Hey, @{join.mention} you are #{join.position} person in this server!
Make sure to check out #welcome for details on the server and the bot.

joinMessages.Applause: Let's give a warm round of applause to the newest member of the server, {join.mention}!
